# 项目介绍

Jetpack Compose Record Wave

1. 耳机插入检测
2. 实时录制音频，并展示一个波形图
3. 因为我的需求原因，我设置了只有插入耳机才可以录制，并且选择性保存PCM文件


1. Earphone insertion detection
2. Record audio in real-time and display a waveform diagram
3. Due to my requirements, I have set the option to record only when headphones are inserted and selectively save PCM files